    "# 🎨 TOONIFY — Complete LoRA Training Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "**Trains a custom Arcane-style LoRA on top of `nitrosocke/mo-di-diffusion` (SD 1.5)**\n",
    "\n",
    "### Workflow\n",
    "| Cell | Step | Time |\n",
    "|------|------|------|\n",
    "| 0 | Environment check + Drive mount | 1 min |\n",
    "| 1 | Install dependencies | 3–5 min |\n",
    "| 2 | Download base model | 5–10 min |\n",
    "| 3 | Generate 30 real training images | 15–20 min |\n",
    "| 4 | Prepare dataset (validate + caption) | 1 min |\n",
    "| 5 | Configure accelerate + train LoRA | 45–90 min |\n",
    "| 6 | Test the trained LoRA | 2 min |\n",
    "| 7 | Save to Drive + push to GitHub | 2 min |\n",
    "| 8 | Cleanup VRAM | 30 sec |\n",
    "\n",
    "> ⚠️ **Use a T4 or better GPU runtime.** Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU\n"
   ]
  },
